- `/workspace/src/index.js` - The only file requiring modification; contains the stub to be replaced with all three function implementations.
- `/workspace/tests/index.test.js` - The test suite defining the exact expected behavior; read-only reference for correctness.
- `/workspace/README.md` - The specification document describing each function's contract; read-only reference for requirements.
